title: Daily Wire Backstage: 2020 State of the Union Edition
description:
How many home runs will Trump hit during the SOTU? Will viewers be able to actually hear his speech over the Dems booing, hysterical crying, and banging their heads on the floor? After the speech, will Pelosi and Schiff both go full "Raiders of the Lost Ark" melted soldier face? 

Join this roundtable discussion featuring @Ben Shapiro, @Andrew Klavan, @Michael Knowles, and Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing as they get to the bottom of these questions and more.
